Since Confluence 5.x, lucene search only return 500 results and it has affected our [Reporting plugin|https://marketplace.atlassian.com/plugins/net.customware.confluence.plugin.reporting]. Atlassian has suggested to implement the pagination mechanism but it defeats the core functionality of Reporting plugin; since Reporting works by retrieving full set of result from Lucene and perform custom filtering for report generation. 

Is there any alternative way on going around this without affecting how our plugin works?

