Permission check are a expensive operation and it may affect performance in instances with a high number of users and groups.

The page tree macro check permissions for every page to be included in the macro, which in certain cases can take a long time.

There could be an option to display the whole page tree (only page titles) without any permission check. Permissions should still apply if a user clicks on a link to a page in the macro.
